    "href": "https://tapsigner.com/"
  }, "Tapsigners"), " are great multisig tool as you can easily back them up and keep your keys cold whilst still being able to quickly use them alongside nunchuck on your phone.|")), mdx("h2", null, "The Kicker"), mdx("p", null, "Collaborative MultiSigs are a new magic human layer on top of magical internet money. Multisigs combine psychology, modern organisation theory and sound money to create something we the world has never seen before. MultiSig Magic Trust Machines will be a core part of the future, and the bitcoin economy."), mdx("p", null, "For me, it is the unspent bitcoin which can make an unspent.space strong.. Now it is up to you to create your own Magic MultiSig Trust Machine and continue the story."));
